title: John Zorn 's Essential Cinema (2008) [FLAC]
description:
John Zorn's Essential Cinema live at "Radical Jewish Music Festival", International House, Philadelphia, PA, March 2nd, 2008

Line Up:

John Zorn: Alto Sax
Marc Ribot: Guitar
Jamie Saft: Rhodes, Organ
Trevor Dunn: Bass
Kenny Wolleson: Vibes
Joey Baron: Drums
Cyro Baptista: Percussion
Ikue Mori: Laptop
Erik Friedlander: Cello

1. Rose Hobart (Full Band, minus Friedlander)
2. Go Go Go (Zorn, Dunn, Baron)
3. Oz: The Tin Woodman's Dream (Ikue Mori Solo)
4. Ritual In Transfigured Time (Full Band)
